                        <h1 class="settings-title">‚öôÔ∏è Ayarlar</h1>
                        <p style="opacity: 0.9; font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 0;">Hesap ayarlarƒ±nƒ±zƒ± y√∂netin</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="settings-card">
                        <div class="settings-card-header">
                            üë§ Profil Bilgileri
